-- Fanuc to Double Production With New Japan Plant, Nikkei Says
-- B y   J a c o b   A d e l m a n
-- 2012-02-12T08:34:35Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-02-12/fanuc-to-double-production-with-new-japan-plant-nikkei-says.html
Fanuc Corp. (6954)  plans to build a new
factory in Ibaraki Prefecture to double its production of
 machine tools  to 5,000 units a month, the Nikkei newspaper
reported.  The increase comes amid rising demand for tools used in the
manufacture of key smartphone components, the newspaper reported
today without saying where it got the information.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Jacob Adelman in Tokyo at 
